---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Use | ARED Furniture Repair"
  description="Terms of use for the ARED Furniture Repair & Antique Restoration website. Read our terms governing website usage and services."
  canonicalPath="/terms-of-use/"
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Terms of Use', url: '/terms-of-use/' }]}
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-wood texture-wood py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-cream font-bold">Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-cream/60 text-sm">Last updated: March 5, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-8 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing and using the ARED Furniture Repair & Antique Restoration website
            (aredrepair.com), you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not
            agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Use of Website</h2>
          <p>
            This website is provided for informational purposes about our furniture repair and
            restoration services. You agree to use this website only for lawful purposes and in a
            manner that does not infringe upon or restrict the use of this website by others.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>Use the website in any way that could damage, disable, or impair it</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the website</li>
            <li>Use automated tools to scrape or collect information from the website</li>
            <li>Transmit any harmful code, viruses, or malicious software</li>
            <li>Use the website to send unsolicited communications</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Services and Estimates</h2>
          <p>
            Information about our services, including descriptions and general pricing guidance, is
            provided for informational purposes only. All estimates are provided after individual
            assessment of each piece of furniture. Final pricing may vary based on the actual
            condition and scope of work required.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            A verbal or written estimate does not constitute a binding contract until both parties
            agree to the terms of service for a specific project.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on this website, including text, images, logos, and design elements, is the
            property of ARED Furniture Repair & Antique Restoration or its content providers and is
            protected by applicable copyright and trademark laws. You may not reproduce, distribute,
            or use any content from this website without our prior written consent.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Photos and Portfolio</h2>
          <p>
            Photos displayed on our website, including before and after images in our portfolio,
            represent actual work performed by ARED Furniture Repair & Antique Restoration. Results
            may vary for each individual project based on the condition, age, and material of the
            furniture.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            This website is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis. We make no warranties,
            expressed or implied, regarding the website's accuracy, reliability, or availability. We
            do not warrant that the website will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or
            other harmful components.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, ARED Furniture Repair & Antique Restoration
            shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages
            arising from your use of this website or inability to use it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>
            Our website may contain links to third-party websites for your convenience. We do not
            endorse or assume responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any
            third-party sites.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms of Use shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the
            State of Texas, without regard to its conflict of law provisions. Any disputes arising
            from these terms shall be resolved in the courts of Collin County, Texas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Use at any time. Changes will be posted on
            this page with an updated date. Your continued use of the website after changes are
            posted constitutes your acceptance of the revised terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-wood mb-3">Contact Information</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about these Terms of Use, please contact us:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-charcoal">Phone:</strong>
              <a href="tel:+12146826371" class="text-gold hover:text-gold-dark">(214) 682-6371</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-charcoal">Address:</strong> 10 Regency Dr Bldg B, Wylie, TX 75098
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
